#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:2
msgid "Google Cloud Bigtable"
msgstr "谷歌云 Bigtable"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:7
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:9
msgid ""
"Google Cloud Bigtable is a petabyte-scale, fully managed NoSQL database. "
"Integrating Cloud Bigtable as a built-in remote storage connector inside "
"LMCache bridges volatile high-cost in-memory tiers (Redis) and low-cost, "
"high-latency archival object stores (S3)."
msgstr "Google Cloud Bigtable 是一个 PB 级别的完全托管的 NoSQL 数据库。将 Cloud Bigtable 作为 LMCache 内置的远程存储连接器集成，可以桥接高成本的易失性内存层（Redis）和低成本、高延迟的归档对象存储（S3）。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:11
msgid ""
"For more information, see the `Cloud Bigtable Overview "
"<https://cloud.google.com/bigtable/docs/overview>`_ and `Cloud Bigtable "
"Pricing <https://cloud.google.com/bigtable/pricing>`_."
msgstr "有关更多信息，请参阅 `Cloud Bigtable 概述 <https://cloud.google.com/bigtable/docs/overview>`_ 和 `Cloud Bigtable 定价 <https://cloud.google.com/bigtable/pricing>`_。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:14
msgid "Architecture & Payload Limits"
msgstr "架构与负载限制"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:16
msgid ""
"**Chunk Size Optimization**: Set LMCache's logical ``chunk_size`` to "
"**256 tokens**. This groups payloads to minimize sequential Point-Read "
"gRPC calls, preventing Python event-loop (GIL) bottlenecks."
msgstr "**块大小优化**：将 LMCache 的逻辑 ``chunk_size`` 设置为 **256 个 token**。这将对有效负载进行分组，以最小化顺序 Point-Read gRPC 调用，防止 Python 事件循环 (GIL) 瓶颈。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:17
msgid ""
"**MutateRow Limit**: Enforces a strict **90.0 MB request limit** for a "
"single ``MutateRow`` gRPC request."
msgstr "**MutateRow 限制**：对单个 ``MutateRow`` gRPC 请求强制执行严格的 **90.0 MB 请求限制**。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:18
msgid ""
"**Storage Tier Row Limits**: The **SSD Tier** ceiling is **100 MiB per "
"cell/row**. The **Enterprise Plus In-Memory Tier** is limited to **1.0 "
"MiB per row**."
msgstr "**存储层行限制**：**SSD 层**的上限为**每个单元/行 100 MiB**。**企业增强内存层**的限制为**每行 1.0 MiB**。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:19
msgid ""
"**TTLCache Shielding**: Embeds a thread-safe ``TTLCache`` (10-second TTL "
"default) to shield Bigtable nodes from concurrent prefetch lookup spikes."
msgstr "**TTLCache 保护**: 嵌入一个线程安全的 ``TTLCache``（默认 TTL 为 10 秒），以保护 Bigtable 节点免受并发预取查找峰值的影响。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:22
msgid "Infrastructure Setup"
msgstr "基础设施设置"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:24
msgid "**1. Enable GCP APIs**"
msgstr "**1. 启用 GCP API**"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:28
msgid ""
"gcloud services enable bigtable.googleapis.com "
"bigtableadmin.googleapis.com --project=your-gcp-project-id"
msgstr "gcloud services enable bigtable.googleapis.com bigtableadmin.googleapis.com --project=your-gcp-project-id"

