#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:115
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "身份验证"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:117
msgid ""
"**Application Default Credentials (ADC)**: If ``credentials_path`` is "
"omitted or ``null``, the connector natively invokes ADC. Compatible with "
"local development via ``gcloud auth application-default login`` or GKE "
"Workload Identity Federation."
msgstr "**应用默认凭据 (ADC)**：如果 ``credentials_path`` 被省略或为 ``null``，连接器将原生调用 ADC。支持通过 ``gcloud auth application-default login`` 进行本地开发或 GKE 工作负载身份联合。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache/storage_backends/bigtable.rst:118
msgid ""
"**Explicit Keys**: Pass the absolute filesystem path containing a mounted"
" GCP Service Account JSON secret to ``credentials_path``."
msgstr "**显式密钥**：将包含挂载的 GCP 服务账户 JSON 密钥的绝对文件系统路径传递给 ``credentials_path``。"

